# General patterns for future reproducers
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/*.so
**/*.dll
**/*.pdb
**/*.exe

# Large crash artifacts — keep only summaries (gdb.log), never binary cores or handler logs
**/crash/core
**/crash/core.*
**/crash/handler.log
